files.help:
python-jupyter_core < v5.0.0:
export JUPYTER_CONFIG_DIR="$XDG_CONFIG_HOME"/jupyter
v5.0.0 <= python-jupyter_core < v6.0.0:
export JUPYTER_PLATFORM_DIRS="1" (see [180])
python-jupyter_core >= v6.0.0: full support (via python-platformdirs) enabled by default
_Relevant issue_: https://github.com/jupyter/jupyter_core/issues/185
